Installation
------------

You can choose between different installation methods.

### Classic method ###

- Build and install:

        $ make
        # make install

- Uninstall:

        # make uninstall


### Debian package ###

- Build and install:

        $ make debian_pkg
        # dpkg -i @executable_name@_@version@_all.deb

- Uninstall:

        # apt purge snapman


### Arch Linux package

- Build and install:

        $ make arch_pkg
        # pacman -U @executable_name@-@version@-1--any.pkg.tar.xz

- Uninstall:

        # pacman -Rsc snapman
